- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The proposed algorithm can be considered as an AI technique for anomaly detection. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics): The paper involves the use of graph theory and $K$-NN graphs for anomaly detection, which can be considered as a topic in discrete mathematics. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The proposed algorithm can be applied to high-dimensional data, which can include image data. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): Anomaly detection is an important topic in security, and the proposed algorithm can be applied to detect anomalies in security-related data.
